items.name: Teleflora's Wonderful Whimsy Bouquet
items.description: Capture the magic of spring with this wondrous rose bouquet, artfully arranged in a pearlescent white glass vase.
items.arrangement: Blush roses, pink alstroemeria, pink carnations, miniature light yellow carnations and pink sinuata statice are arranged with huckleberry and parvifolia eucalyptus. Delivered in a Wonderful Whimsy cylinder.

items.name: Teleflora's Sweet Hummingbird Bouquet
items.description: Inspired by a vintage flea market find, this charming glass cube is adorned with delightful botanical hummingbird imagery and filled with an equally enchanting rose bouquet.
items.arrangement: This beautiful bouquet includes hot pink spray roses, dark pink alstroemeria, lavender cushion spray chrysanthemums, pink carnations, miniature pink carnations, leatherleaf fern and pitta negra. Delivered in a Sweet Hummingbird cube.

items.name: Precious Pink Tulips
items.description: Beautiful and "simply said" light pink tulips are a hip way to show you care.
items.arrangement: Ten delicate light pink Tulips arranged in a clear glass vase.

items.name: Full Of Love Bouquet
items.description: Spring into pink! Delicate roses, tulips and carnations fill a graceful vase with a cheerful expression of your love. It's affection perfection!
items.arrangement: Includes pink roses, tulips, carnations and waxflower, accented with fresh pitta negra and variegated pittosporum. Delivered in a lovely glass vase.

items.name: Teleflora's Lovely Shine Bouquet
items.description: This sparkling gift takes Mother's Day glam to a whole new level! Playful pink and lavender blooms are arranged with a desert-inspired succulent in a sparkling mosaic glass vase.
items.arrangement: This chic bouquet features light pink roses, purple alstroemeria, miniature lavender carnations, dark pink sweet william, lavender sinuata statice, dusty miller, huckleberry and a large green echeveria succulent plant. Delivered in a Shining Beauty cylinder.

items.name: Teleflora's Playful Springtime Daffodil Bouquet
items.description: A playful arrangement of sunny daffodils and rich purple asters in a keepsake cube, this gorgeous gift celebrates spring in a most joyful way!
items.arrangement: Yellow daffodils and lavender matsumoto asters are arranged with bupleurum and variegated pittosporum. Delivered in a Sunshine Color Splash Cube.

items.name: Make a Wish
items.description: A summery mix of yellow daisy chrysanthemums, purple asters and red and orange carnations - arranged in a clear ginger vase and adorned with a cheerful green plaid bow - will make their wishes come true!
items.arrangement: Yellow daisy spray chrysanthemums, purple Matsumoto asters, red miniature carnations, orange carnations and alstroemeria - accented with bupleurum - are delivered in a miniature ginger vase adorned with a plaid green ribbon.

items.name: Teleflora's Possibly Pink
items.description: Impossibly pretty. This decidedly feminine arrangement is absolutely delightful.
items.arrangement: Perfectly peachy peach spray roses, pink asiatic lilies and miniature carnations, lavender cushion spray chrysanthemums and waxflower, pittosporum and seeded eucalyptus fill an exclusive pink cube. Have one delivered and almost anything's possible.

items.name: Teleflora's Pleasing Purple Bouquet
items.description: These luxurious lavender roses and crisp white lilies are poised to please! Perfectly presented in a stylish cube vase, it's an any-occasion surprise they'll never forget!
items.arrangement: Lavender roses, white asiatic lilies, purple carnations, lavender carnations, purple button spray chrysanthemums and lavender button spray chrysanthemums are arranged with lavender limonium and pitta negra. Delivered in a glass cube.

items.name: Teleflora's Dancing Beauty Bouquet
items.description: Dance into Mother's Day with this beautiful ballet pink surprise! Feminine roses and lilies brighten her special day in a keepsake vase of European glass with metallic finish.
items.arrangement: Pink roses, hot pink spray roses, white alstroemeria, pink asiatic lilies, miniature pink carnations and lavender sinuata statice are arranged with leatherleaf fern. Delivered in a Dancing Beauty vase.

items.name: Teleflora's Pretty Pastel Bouquet
items.description: Oh so soft and divinely delicate, this perfect pastel bouquet is pretty as can be. Delivered in a classic ginger jar, the graceful arrangement of alstroemeria, carnations and stock is a welcome surprise on any occasion.
items.arrangement: This pretty arrangement includes lavender alstroemeria, pink carnations, miniature pink carnations, pink stock, purple sinuata statice, parvifolia eucalyptus, and seeded eucalyptus. Delivered in a Clear Glass Ginger Jar.

items.name: Teleflora's Garden Romance
items.description: Hello, gorgeous! This lovely bouquet includes purple hydrangea, light pink spray roses and white asiatic lilies arranged in our vibrant violet glass cube.
items.arrangement: Purple hydrangea, light pink spray roses, white asiatic lilies, dark pink alstroemeria and lavender sinuata statice are accented with assorted greens. Delivered in Teleflora's glass violet cube.

items.name: Love and Laughter
items.description: Know someone you love to make laugh? Someone you love to laugh with? Someone who could use a laugh? Someone who fits all of the above? Well, this beautiful arrangement has charms that extend way beyond its blossoms.
items.arrangement: Lavender roses and daisy spray chrysanthemums, purple carnations, miniature carnations, matsumoto asters and pink waxflower are delivered in a sweet lilac vase that's tied with a purple satin ribbon. Love, laugh and send it today!

items.name: Teleflora's Luxe Leaves Plant
items.description: Give the gift of style! Inspired by mid-century design, this modern ceramic planter on a sleek wooden base is the perfect presentation for the sculptural beauty of a lush zanzibar plant.
items.arrangement: This live gift features a Zanzibar gem plant arranged with white pebbles and sheet moss. Delivered in Teleflora's Mid Mod Geometric planter.

items.name: How Sweet It Is
items.description: How sweet it will be when this dazzling arrangement arrives at someone's door. Very vibrant. Very vivacious. And very, very pretty.
items.arrangement: Light orange roses, orange spray roses, and matsumoto asters, hot pink miniature carnations and more are delivered in a lovely glass vase. Be sweet and send this one today!

items.name: Teleflora's Send A Shimmer Bouquet
items.description: Shimmer and shine! Show her the sparkle of your love with this loving gift of classic red roses in a shimmering mosaic glass vase.
items.arrangement: Red roses, red spray roses, red carnations, miniature red carnations and red alstroemeria are accented with seeded eucalyptus, huckleberry and lemon leaf. Delivered in a Love Sparkles vase.

items.name: Teleflora's Go Glam Bouquet
items.description: Go for the glam this Valentine's Day with a luxurious bouquet of red and pink blooms presented in a shimmering mosaic glass keepsake vase.
items.arrangement: This bouquet features red roses, miniature red carnations, pink alstroemeria, white cushion spray chrysanthemums, pink sinuata statice, leatherleaf fern, parvifolia eucalyptus, lemon leaf and dusty miller. Delivered in a Love Sparkles vase.

items.name: Teleflora's Desert Sunrise Bouquet
items.description: Peaceful yet energizing, this unforgettable arrangement of desert-hued blooms and succulents in a sleek bamboo cube is a chic gift on any special occasion.
items.arrangement: Peach roses, white asiatic lilies, peach miniature carnations, and white stock are accented with pitta negra, dusty miller, and a green echeveria succulent. Delivered in a Small Natural Bamboo Cube.

items.name: Isle of White
items.description: Like a vacation for the senses, this lovely bouquet delivers an oasis of beauty and elegance. Soothing, serene and very special.
items.arrangement: Crème roses, white asiatic lilies and stock stem are incredibly arranged in a bubble vase. When it comes to bouquets, this is definitely the right way to do white.

items.name: Teleflora's Vintage Butterfly Bouquet
items.description: Make mom's spirit soar with this vintage-inspired vase, adorned with whimsical butterflies and bursting with the prettiest pink rose and daisy bouquet!
items.arrangement: Hot pink roses, purple button spray chrysanthemums, lavender cushion spray chrysanthemums, white daisy spray chrysanthemums and raspberry sinuata statice ar arranged with leatherleaf fern and huckleberry. Delivered in Teleflora's Vintage Butterfly Cube.

items.name: Fashionista Blooms
items.description: This arrangement would be perfect for any girl with an eye for style. It's a must-have for fashionistas everywhere.
items.arrangement: Gorgeous green hydrangea, yellow and light pink roses, pink spray roses and mini gerberas, light yellow carnations and green button spray chrysanthemums are delivered in a pretty gathering vase. Not just any vase, of course, this one's accessorized with a chartreuse taffeta ribbon and pink raffia.

items.name: Teleflora's Citrus Smiles Bouquet
items.description: They brighten your days with their friendship and love, brighten theirs with these bold and beautiful blooms! Hand-delivered in a stylish glass cube, a gift in and of itself - this spirited mix of roses, carnations and mums is sure to make them smile!
items.arrangement: Bold orange roses, green carnations, dark pink miniature carnations, and yellow button spray chrysanthemums are mixed with ming fern and lemon leaf. Delivered in a glass cube.

items.name: Cascading Elegance Bouquet
items.description: A dramatic display in jewel-toned roses and hydrangea in a sophisticated vase, this majestic bouquet will take their breath away.
items.arrangement: Dark pink hydrangea, lavender hydrangea, lavender roses, light lavender roses, red roses, red spray roses, purple carnations, purple button spray chrysanthemums, and purple cushion spray chrysanthemums are arranged with hanging green amaranthus, israeli ruscus, xanadu philodendron leaves, and red ti leaves. Delivered in a glass romanesque vase.

items.name: Teleflora's Lush and Lovely
items.description: "Lush and lovely" might seem like a bit of an understatement when gazing at this incredible arrangement of luxurious flowers delivered in a divine Mercury Glass Bowl. Let's add "beautiful and breathtaking" to the description.
items.arrangement: Spectacular red cymbidium orchids, purple mokara orchids, lavender hydrangea, crème roses, dark red spray roses, burgundy dahlias, purple and lavender chrysanthemums and burgundy copper beech arrive in an exclusive Mercury Glass Bowl.
